{"id":"6a673b7f-d4d8-451e-8d20-3de67765e321","name":"Nymphopocalypse","description":"<h4 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(165, 0, 171, 0.44); color: inherit\">In a big city, an outbreak of a mysterious virus that turns women into nymphomaniacs In a big city, an outbreak of a mysterious virus that turns women into nymphomaniacs appears and causes the biggest chaos and whoredom in history!</mark></span></h4><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); color: inherit\">Yeah it's a parody of Dying Light, I really loved the game so I wanted to make something as inspiration, have fun 👍</mark></em></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(173, 0, 179, 0.518); color: inherit\">Mutations/Variations</mark></strong></span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.686); color: inherit\">Raper</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/62a9c898-64c8-4bcc-8e1d-a4d13520ba7b_acb4fb3f-7336-4dcb-a75d-85ec3329d680.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ff0000; color: inherit\">It is the most common, runs around like crazy and rapes any man she sees.</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 8, 255, 0.533); color: inherit\">Tittiefucker</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/62a9c898-64c8-4bcc-8e1d-a4d13520ba7b_b23a2894-60cc-48d6-abb6-a798e51844b7.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><span style=\"color: